داشبورد شخصی — Personal Dashboard
=================================
Run: dashboard-shakhsi   (or find "داشبورد شخصی" in the app grid)

Data file (auto-saved on every change):
  ~/.local/share/dashboard-shakhsi/data.json
Back up that one file to keep all your tasks and finance records.

Exports (MD/CSV/JSON/TXT) are written to ~/Downloads.
Debug: dashboard-shakhsi --devtools
Uninstall: sudo apt remove dashboard-shakhsi  (data file is kept)
